{{Cite web |url=https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2019/1212/2019121200784_c.pdf |title=完成收購 SKINS 品牌全球商標及專利  |access-date=2019-12-12 |archive-date=2019-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210504091548/https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2019/1212/2019121200784_c.pdf |dead-url=no }}
